name: Rash
title: Rash
description: This value set may undergo changes until the HL7 Multiple Chronic Care FHIR IG is formally published in 2024.
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values reflect patients experiencing rash, an area of irritated, swollen skin with eruptions on it.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this value set is to identify patients experiencing Rash.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes Rash related SNOMED CT codes from Findings and Disorder hierarchy.),(Exclusion Criteria: None.)
